aryonic feedback processes is included. In addition, we discuss the central DM distribution of DDO 210 whose stellar mass is relatively low in our sample to examine the scenario of inefficient supernova feedback in low mass dwarf galaxies predicted from recent {$\Lambda$}CDM SPH simulations of dwarf galaxies where central cusps still remain.},
